snippet.title: The Spy Who Shrunk Me Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist The Spy Who Shrunk Me now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/754850/The_Spy_Who_Shrunk_Me/ 

Step into the shoes of Audrey Smoothspy in this stealth game where you are equipped with a shrink ray and some banana peels! Crush the cold war communists under your heel in this exciting new title from the cool cats of Catland. 

Learn more at https://catland.studio.
